         <abstract id="aspace_8351727935f564736e505435c0e036e5">The records consist of memoranda and reports documenting the activities and operations of the Faculty of Yale College. Included are minutes from meetings of the faculty and executive committee, committee reports, attendance books, committee membership lists, and financial papers.</abstract>
